  <brief_title>A Survey on the Rate of Glucose Intolerance in Hong Kong Chinese</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Survey on the Rate of Glucose Intolerance in Hong Kong Chinese: Validation of the Chinese University Diabetes Screening Score</official_title>
  <sponsors>
