  <source>Chinese University of Hong Kong</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: There is a high rate of glucose intolerance among Hong Kong Chinese.

      The investigators plan to screen Hong Kong Chinese from the community with oral glucose
      tolerance test (OGTT). The subjects will be referred from GP centers in the community and
      self-referred with public advertisement on this survey.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
